message: Professor Dr. Niaz Ahmad Akhtar (SI) holds a PhD in Chemical Engineering from the University of Leeds, UK. He has done his undergraduate in Chemical Engineering from University of the Punjab. Previously, Dr. Niaz has served as the Vice Chancellor of the University of Engineering and Technology (UET) Taxila, and as the rector of the National Textile University, Faisalabad.
